query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mi_idx t mi) NoHashJoin(mi mi_idx t mc) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS mainstream_movie
from title AS t
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Drama',
'Horror',
'Western',
'Family')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id;
